uk.co.strangeskies.reflection

Interface Reified<S extends Reified<S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of the instance
    All Superinterfaces:
    Copyable<S>, Self<S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TypedObject, TypeParameter, TypeToken

    public interface Reified<S extends Reified<S>>
extends Self<S>
    A type whose instances know their own type, including any available generic information.

    As with the extended Self interface, generally only the most specific useful type will be considered.

    • Method Detail

      • getThisType

        TypeToken<S> getThisType()
        Returns:
        The accurate type of the instance, accounting for generics. It is up to the implementation whether the returned type is also completely specific - in other words, the type may mention wildcards or inference variables if the exact type cannot be determined.
